data.description: Now's the time to make this 2007 Energy Star bi-level home your family home. Located in a quiet, family friendly and welcoming neighborhood.  Conveniently located between Eau Claire and Chippewa Falls on approximately a 1/2 acre corner lot giving the kids and pets plenty of room to play . Close to the Hallie ball fields and shopping. Includes 3 bedroom and 2 full baths.  Large primary bedroom with a walk in closet and a vanity with sink.  Open concept design on the upper level.  Large lower level rec room and for all those family gatherings with a sliding door for easy access to the yard from downstairs.  3 car attached insulated and heated garage with access to the basement /laundry room. Sprinkler system and beautiful landscaping for easy maintenance. Let me help you make this your new home and start building your memories.  Basketball hoop included.  Freezer and fridge in basement excluded.    Buyer and buyer's agent to verify measurements.
